data.description: Welcome to your dream oasis! This lovely home offers a perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and functionality. Nestled within a serene neighborhood, this property is a true gem that caters to every aspect of gracious living. The heart of the home is the magnificent great room, where relaxation and entertainment seamlessly come together. Picture yourself unwinding by the fireplace on cozy evenings, with the wood laminate floors underfoot adding a touch of warmth. This space effortlessly flows into the gourmet island kitchen, a culinary enthusiast's dream. The kitchen boasts plenty of cabinet space to neatly organize all your essentials, while the central island stands as a focal point for meal preparation. For those who value outdoor living, the large covered patio is a true masterpiece. Overlooking a glistening pool, this outdoor haven invites you to enjoy al fresco dining, lounging, and hosting unforgettable gatherings. Retreat to the expansive owner's suite, a private sanctuary that redefines luxury. The corner jetted tub beckons you to unwind and indulge, offering a spa-like experience right at home. A separate shower adds convenience and elegance to your routine. With abundant space, this suite ensures your comfort and privacy. Working from home is a pleasure in the dedicated home office, where productivity meets sophistication. Whether you're wrapping up tasks or seeking inspiration, this space is designed to cater to your professional needs. Throughout the home, natural light bathes each room, creating an inviting and vibrant atmosphere. Every corner is thoughtfully designed to offer both practicality and aesthetic delight, making this residence an embodiment of refined living.
